4. Click "Subflows" in the top left then cilck "New Subflow". Name it "Jump".

5. Copy and paste the following code block into the new Jump subflow.
```
MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Space}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 150 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
SET MoveCounter TO 0
Variables.GenerateRandomNumber.RandomNumber MinimumValue: 175 MaximumValue: 250 RandomNumber=> Limit
```

6. Save all changes.

7. That should do it. Run the flow while you are logged in to the game and your mouse is focused within the game window. It will send a spacebar every 2-5 minutes. If you get disconnected, it will attempt to log you back in automatically.
